WEBVTT

00:00.219 --> 00:02.895
So, some brands are cutting the Amazon cord...

00:03.185 --> 00:08.336
...to focus on what's known as direct-to-consumer selling, such as Nike.

00:09.709 --> 00:13.590
Nike's loyalty scheme allows it to create customer profiles...

00:13.806 --> 00:16.313
...of its 250 million members,...

00:16.691 --> 00:19.613
...70 million of whom joined during the pandemic.

00:20.244 --> 00:23.847
Nike's apps offer the customer a personalized experience...

00:24.105 --> 00:27.461
...in return for a detailed insight into their behavior.

00:27.940 --> 00:31.523
Nike's apps let users customize their own shoes...

00:31.761 --> 00:35.457
...and in doing so learn the customer's favorite colors and designs,....

00:35.856 --> 00:37.627
...and by tracking how far they run,...

00:37.855 --> 00:42.945
...can even let the customer know when it's time to splash out on a new pair of shoes.

